# KeyboardSwap Roadmap

This roadmap defines the implementation order for KeyboardSwap.

The goal is to always build the strongest foundation before moving on to more advanced features.

---

# Phase 1 - Marketplace MVP

Goal:
Launch a trustworthy marketplace where users can buy and sell keyboard-related items through curated auctions.

## Accounts

- User authentication
- Profiles
- Seller pages
- Builder role support (future)

## Listings

- Dynamic listing form
- Category-specific attributes
- Image uploads
- Listing approval
- Listing scheduling
- Edit listings
- Delete listings
- My Listings

## Marketplace

- Browse listings
- Search
- Category pages
- Dynamic filters
- Homepage
- Featured listings

## Auctions

- Live countdown
- Proxy bidding
- Reserve prices
- Buy It Now
- Bid increments
- Anti-sniping
- Auction history
- Sold archive

## Administration

- Listing review queue
- Featured listings
- Brand approval
- Product approval
- User moderation

---

# Phase 2 - Transactions

Goal:
Create a trusted buying experience.

## Orders

- Winning bidder workflow
- Checkout
- Stripe integration
- Escrow support
- Shipping tracking
- Transaction history

## Ratings

- Buyer ratings
- Seller ratings
- Rating tags
- Reputation score

## Notifications

- Outbid
- Auction won
- Payment received
- Item shipped
- Questions
- Rating reminders

---

# Phase 3 - Community

Goal:
Make KeyboardSwap a place users visit every day.

## Collections

- Current collection
- Wishlist
- Dream builds
- Previously owned
- Parts bin

## Profiles

- Public collections
- Recent purchases
- Recent sales
- Favorite builds

## Verified Builds

- Community submissions
- Admin verification
- Build galleries
- Sound tests
- Typing tests

## Questions

- Public Q&A
- Seller responses
- Helpful answers

---

# Phase 4 - Builder Marketplace

Goal:
Connect enthusiasts with professional builders.

## Builder Profiles

- Portfolio
- Gallery
- Pricing
- Specialties
- Ratings
- Verification

## Build Requests

- Customer requests
- Builder quotes
- Quote comparison
- Builder selection

## Projects

- Progress tracking
- Timeline
- Progress photos
- Escrow
- Completion workflow

---

# Phase 5 - Keyboard Builder

Goal:
Create the best keyboard planning tool available.

## Compatibility

- Cases
- PCBs
- Plates
- Stabilizers
- Switches
- Keycaps

## Build Planner

- Create builds
- Save builds
- Clone builds
- Share builds

## Marketplace Integration

- Build using marketplace listings
- Suggest compatible alternatives
- Show estimated total cost
- One-click purchase

---

# Phase 6 - Market Intelligence

Goal:
Become the authority on keyboard values.

## Price History

- Historical sale prices
- Average sale price
- Highest sale
- Lowest sale
- Market trends

## Saved Searches

- Email alerts
- New listing alerts
- Price drop alerts

## Analytics

- Most watched
- Most bid
- Trending brands
- Popular layouts

---

# Phase 7 - Platform Growth

Goal:
Grow the KeyboardSwap ecosystem.

Potential future features:

- Mobile app
- API
- Discord integration
- YouTube creator pages
- Builder certification
- Marketplace insights
- Premium memberships
- International shipping tools
- Vendor partnerships

---

# Guiding Principles

Every feature should strengthen one or more of the following pillars:

- Marketplace
- Community
- Tools

Every feature should increase trust.

Every feature should improve marketplace data.

Every feature should improve compatibility knowledge.

KeyboardSwap should become the operating system for the mechanical keyboard hobby.